1
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:22,320
It's finally settled.

2
00:01:22,440 --> 00:01:23,600
Su Manyun and Lu Jingxi

3
00:01:23,600 --> 00:01:25,039
both lost their shares in the Lu family.

4
00:01:25,039 --> 00:01:28,280
They will never make waves in the Lu family again.

5
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:31,680
This way, your position in Lu Group is secure.

6
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,680
I'm sorry.

7
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:54,680
I didn't mean to keep it from you.

8
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:57,960
The reason I didn't tell you about these plans

9
00:01:58,720 --> 00:01:59,680
is because I didn't want

10
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:02,120
to drag you into my family's mess.

11
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,920
Taking down Su Manyun

12
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,000
and helping you secure the Lu family

13
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:09,080
is the only thing I could think of doing for you.

14
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:09,759
If you feel

15
00:02:09,759 --> 00:02:11,280
that I was just using you from the beginning,

16
00:02:11,280 --> 00:02:13,080
you can choose to end this at any time.

17
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:14,280
I have no objections.

18
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,120
Do you think what I care about

19
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,800
is being used by you?

20
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,600
You can get a good night's sleep now.

21
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:21,840
Shen Jingyao finally got the punishment he deserved.

22
00:03:23,040 --> 00:03:25,840
The revenge for the original host's murdered mother

23
00:03:25,840 --> 00:03:27,640
and the suffering from his abuse

24
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,210
have finally been settled.

25
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,880
As for those who aided him,

26
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:36,520
Su Manyun and her son didn't end up well either.

27
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:38,040
But,

28
00:03:39,760 --> 00:03:40,720
why?

29
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:44,660
Why haven't I returned to my original timeline?

30
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:51,800
Young Madam.

31
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:53,560
Come in.

32
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,120
Young Madam,

33
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:01,400
the master wants you to go to his study.

34
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,200
Well,

35
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:04,800
the master doesn't look well today.

36
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,200
You must be careful when you go there later.

37
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:34,480
Dad, you called me here today

38
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,680
because of my family's affairs, right?

39
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:39,890
It seems you still have some self-awareness.

40
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,159
Shen Zhixia,

41
00:04:42,159 --> 00:04:46,020
what our Lu family needs is a daughter-in-law with a clean background

42
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:48,120
who can help the family,

43
00:04:49,400 --> 00:04:52,320
not a trouble tied to a murderer.

44
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:00,360
Jingheng.

45
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:02,760
Zhixia.

46
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:05,740
Read this carefully, you two.

47
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,480
The lawyer has drafted this agreement.

48
00:05:11,400 --> 00:05:12,480
From now on,

49
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,560
you go your separate ways.

50
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:22,560
Alright.

51
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:25,080
The agreement is fine. I can sign it.

52
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:29,320
You...

53
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:35,200
I don't agree to the divorce agreement.

54
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:36,720
You don't agree?

55
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:39,480
Are you blind or stupid?

56
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,400
Don't you know

57
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,200
what her situation is right now?

58
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:46,159
Her father, Shen Jingyao, is a murderer.

59
00:05:47,080 --> 00:05:49,360
You still want to be tied to her family.

60
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:53,100
Do you think our Lu family doesn't have enough trouble?

61
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:57,320
Dad.

62
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,680
When Zhixia and I got married,

63
00:05:58,680 --> 00:05:59,610
it was your idea.

64
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:02,000
Now it's your idea for us to get divorced.

65
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,730
I won't listen to you this time.

66
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,130
I won't divorce Zhixia.

67
00:06:06,240 --> 00:06:08,370
Are you still a member of the Lu family?

68
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:11,290
Have you considered the Lu family's reputation?

69
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:12,560
The Lu family's reputation?

70
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,880
I will fight for it on my own,

71
00:06:13,880 --> 00:06:15,320
instead of sacrificing my marriage

72
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:16,920
or Zhixia for it.

73
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:19,540
I have made my decision and I won't change it.

74
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:21,200
If you don't accept it,

75
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:24,440
I can leave the Lu Group and start my own business.

76
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:27,720
I will never leave Zhixia again in my life.

77
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:30,080
You are going to piss me off.

78
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,200
For this woman,

79
00:06:33,080 --> 00:06:36,340
you don't even want the inheritance rights of the Lu Group?

80
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,000
I think you're crazy too.

81
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:38,960
I am not crazy.

82
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,400
I know very well

83
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,540
what the most important thing is.

84
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:44,480
You guys...

85
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:53,600
Why did you say such harsh words?

86
00:06:54,159 --> 00:06:55,600
Leaving the Lu family

87
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,720
and giving up the inheritance rights.

88
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:00,720
You've worked so hard in the Lu family for so long.

89
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,560
For me,

90
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:04,960
is it worth it?

91
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,240
Then tell me, what makes it worth it?

92
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:21,880
I just feel that

93
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,000
I'm not worth it.

94
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:36,880
Whether you are worth it,

95
00:07:37,440 --> 00:07:38,320
is up to me.

96
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:43,970
Where are you taking me?

97
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,080
Why did you bring me here?

98
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:53,409
We've known each other for so long,

99
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:55,080
but we've never

100
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:57,159
sat quietly together like this.

101
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,530
What do you think of this place?

102
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,490
It's beautiful.

103
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,540
This is my favorite place.

104
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,480
Whenever I'm in a bad mood,

105
00:08:09,640 --> 00:08:10,520
coming here,

106
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,480
even if I do nothing,

107
00:08:13,400 --> 00:08:15,280
can quickly calm me down.

108
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:19,490
I don't think I've ever seen you like this.

109
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,480
Like what?

110
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:23,000
Before.

111
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:25,720
You always wear such a hard shell,

112
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:27,680
making you so hard to figure out.

113
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,720
I thought in your eyes,

114
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:32,130
my heart was already laid bare.

115
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:39,360
My mom gave me this beach.

116
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:40,720
When I was little,

117
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:43,320
she often brought me here to pick up seashells.

118
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:46,000
You are the first person I brought here.

119
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:47,720
And the only one.

120
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,320
Do you know what I mean?

121
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,860
I don't quite understand.

122
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:01,160
Then I'll make it clearer.

123
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:03,600
Shen Zhixia.

124
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:06,960
I love you.

125
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,420
As long as you're willing,

126
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,720
we can be together forever.

127
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,880
What about our rules?

128
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,680
Can I unilaterally break the contract?

129
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:41,680
No.

130
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:43,320
But,

131
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,520
we can break it together.

132
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:22,680
I'm doomed.

133
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:26,680
I got carried away by the mood and lust.

134
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:38,840
Oh, Shen Zhixia.

135
00:11:39,160 --> 00:11:41,440
You don't even know if you have a future.

136
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:44,360
How can you give one to someone else?

137
00:12:04,680 --> 00:12:06,200
I'm so done.

138
00:12:06,320 --> 00:12:08,920
There's no turning back now.

139
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:10,880
He's already like this.

140
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:15,040
If I say last night was just an accident,

141
00:12:15,280 --> 00:12:17,760
wouldn't I be a total jerk?

142
00:12:39,160 --> 00:12:41,560
Did you sleep well yesterday, young madam?

143
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:44,880
How can sleep be good or bad?

144
00:12:44,880 --> 00:12:46,080
Just slept normally.

145
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:49,880
Shen Zhixia, are you crazy?

146
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:51,940
What nonsense are you talking about?

147
00:12:52,320 --> 00:12:53,720
Are you not feeling well?

148
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:54,680
I'm not.

149
00:12:55,240 --> 00:12:56,370
I'm perfectly fine.

150
00:13:08,640 --> 00:13:09,680
What are you doing?

151
00:13:09,680 --> 00:13:11,120
Buckling your seatbelt.

152
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:12,680
What else could I be doing?

153
00:13:12,680 --> 00:13:13,520
Seatbelt.

154
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,400
Seatbelt.

155
00:13:18,880 --> 00:13:19,880
I'll do it myself.

156
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,280
Okay.

157
00:13:26,360 --> 00:13:27,160
Stop the car.

158
00:13:32,480 --> 00:13:33,360
The weather is quite nice.

159
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,320
I'll go for a run.

160
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:37,680
Zhixia.

161
00:13:43,320 --> 00:13:44,120
Mr. Lu,

162
00:13:44,120 --> 00:13:46,250
do you want to get out and exercise too?

163
00:13:46,520 --> 00:13:48,120
Why would I need to exercise?

164
00:13:51,120 --> 00:13:52,650
Drive and catch up with her.

165
00:14:05,880 --> 00:14:06,760
Run faster.

166
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:12,600
Come on.

167
00:14:19,040 --> 00:14:20,440
Come on, come on, come on.

168
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:25,560
What? What?

169
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,160
Come on! Come on!

170
00:14:27,560 --> 00:14:28,960
Why are you slowing down?

171
00:14:30,280 --> 00:14:31,360
Are you crazy?

172
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:33,560
I'll wait for you at home.

173
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,360
Bye.

174
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:35,800
Drive.

175
00:15:03,880 --> 00:15:05,240
People talk about long-distance relationships.

176
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:06,120
Long-distance relationship?

177
00:15:06,120 --> 00:15:08,360
Mrs. Wang has to take a cab to see Mr. Li.

